  "title": "Sales Assistant/ Store Associate #80444",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesale of Food Service Product</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Assistant/ Store Associate</strong></li><li>Working Location: Temple Street</li><li>Working Hours: 5-6 days (Monday-Friday & Alt Saturday, 9.00am – 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Commission + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Warmly welcome customers and deliver good customer service.</li><li>Help customers locate products, respond to questions, and provide product recommendations.</li><li>Operate the cash register and process transactions accurately across various forms of payment.</li><li>Keep the sales floor and cashier area clean and well organized.</li><li>Stock and replenish merchandise on shelves and displays as needed.</li><li>Support inventory counts and tag new merchandise.</li><li>Handle customer returns and exchanges in a friendly and efficient manner.</li><li>Stay up to date on product knowledge, promotions, and store policies.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Previous retail or cashiering experience is an advantage but not required, training is provided.</li><li>Minimum Nitec or higher.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Able to multitask and work in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Strong attention to detail and accuracy when handling transactions.</li><li>Positive attitude with a team-player mindset.</li><li>Willing to work on Saturdays.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80444 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
